 effects. This doesn't bother me as much, but I was hoping for some options for surround-sound, coming from a semi-stealth game.Overall I would say this game is about a 4/10 from my view of it within an hour of game-time. I may be missing more good things or bad things about the game, but so far this game wasn't worth it."
