,Recommended,214250,5979433,"Posted: 22 July, 2013",all,mr.sparky,"A great post-apocalyptic survival game that's actually realistic. No zombies or mutants here, just the harsh environment and other people trying to survive.Food, items and ammo are scarce, and it really makes you think about conserving every bullet and morsel of food. Your actions in each situation can have big ramifications. Do you quickly draw your pistol and shoot a thug (and waste a bullet in the process), or threaten him with your loaded pistol and hope he backs off. Do you give your last can of food to a starving survivor, or keep it for yourself for when you need it the most.I found this game thought provoking and it left an emotional impact on me. Highly recommended for anyone wanting to play something more grounded in realism than the usual ""blockbuster"" style action game..."
